11#ifndef MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_AGC2_ADAPTIVE_MODE_LEVEL_ESTIMATOR_H_
12#define MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_AGC2_ADAPTIVE_MODE_LEVEL_ESTIMATOR_H_
13
14#include <stddef.h>
15#include <type_traits>
16
17#include "modules/audio_processing/agc2/agc2_common.h"
18#include "modules/audio_processing/agc2/vad_with_level.h"
19#include "modules/audio_processing/include/audio_processing.h"
20
21namespace webrtc {
22class ApmDataDumper;
23
24// Level estimator for the digital adaptive gain controller.
25class AdaptiveModeLevelEstimator {
26 public:
27 explicit AdaptiveModeLevelEstimator(ApmDataDumper* apm_data_dumper);
28 AdaptiveModeLevelEstimator(const AdaptiveModeLevelEstimator&) = delete;
29 AdaptiveModeLevelEstimator& operator=(const AdaptiveModeLevelEstimator&) =
30 delete;
31 AdaptiveModeLevelEstimator(ApmDataDumper* apm_data_dumper,
32 int adjacent_speech_frames_threshold);
33
34 // Updates the level estimation.
35 void Update(const VadLevelAnalyzer::Result& vad_data);
36 // Returns the estimated speech plus noise level.
37 float level_dbfs() const { return level_dbfs_; }
38 // Returns true if the estimator is confident on its current estimate.
39 bool IsConfident() const;
40
41 void Reset();
42
43 private:
44 // Part of the level estimator state used for check-pointing and restore ops.
45 struct LevelEstimatorState {
46 bool operator==(const LevelEstimatorState& s) const;
47 inline bool operator!=(const LevelEstimatorState& s) const {
48 return !(*this == s);
49 }
50 struct Ratio {
51 float numerator;
52 float denominator;
53 float GetRatio() const;
54 };
55 // TODO(crbug.com/webrtc/7494): Remove time_to_confidence_ms if redundant.
56 int time_to_confidence_ms;
57 Ratio level_dbfs;
58 };
59 static_assert(std::is_trivially_copyable<LevelEstimatorState>::value, "");
60
61 void ResetLevelEstimatorState(LevelEstimatorState& state) const;
62
63 void DumpDebugData() const;
64
65 ApmDataDumper* const apm_data_dumper_;
66
67 const int adjacent_speech_frames_threshold_;
68 LevelEstimatorState preliminary_state_;
69 LevelEstimatorState reliable_state_;
70 float level_dbfs_;
71 int num_adjacent_speech_frames_;
72};
73
74} // namespace webrtc
75
76#endif // MODULES_AUDIO_PROCESSING_AGC2_ADAPTIVE_MODE_LEVEL_ESTIMATOR_H_
